Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:55.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,果真 这个真的是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:05.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因为出生在窑炉里得到窑的正气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没想到会是如此境界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:42.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天 柳乙檀你们两位边首要奉御令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在分院郎厅竞赛里要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣接旨 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是分明说好由李边首就任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为何还要竞赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竞赛只不过是形式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:09.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀他的器具 根本与宫里不相配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你还真是太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:16.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在这个朝鲜 最为贵重而宝贵的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不就是王室白瓷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分院郎厅即是管理王室瓷器的\N最高头领之位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这个财路 要由我们来掌握啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个位置一定要由我们的人来坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去见李边首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李边首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:52.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,天下无敌李边首的自尊心\N看来伤得不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:02.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他只是制作肤浅的器具的市井之徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定要坐上分院郎厅位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:11.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,洗掉今日的耻辱 提高王室瓷器品格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,理应如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:19.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是我说啊 也要做好最坏的打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不相信微臣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是不相信殿下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为何只有你们几个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是还未通知其他陶瓷匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要做出吸引殿下之心的最好的器具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,希望你们能配合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都去了李边首的工坊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:01.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那更要抓紧时间\N为何连炼土工作也没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:04.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人善用的凤山白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李边首大人他们都给拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:19.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他觉得梅花图会不稳定\N李边首不使用凤山白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以说啊 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分明就是在这次竞赛里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想要陷大人於困境的意图呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,剩下的白土就只有宣川白土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:41.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我正想试用宣川白土会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,万万不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是平常还好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放著朗厅之位竞争的重要时期\N怎么能试用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是还有莲玉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你帮李边首数年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你应该很了解他所使用的宣川白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,趁此机会 你就尽情展示你的实力吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,福到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,每个人都充满福气 充满福气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给你 你也受到福气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给你 受福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,果然你的瓷器是充满朴实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此精细而华丽的瓷器\N没人能比得上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:37.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这是表示有自信吗\N看你今日气色不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看起来像我女儿的 漂亮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然会献给殿下白瓷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做的什么白日梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你都这把年龄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别说是女儿 都还没娶妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,青盐的白色 穿著华丽的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人接触过数多王室的瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,无论色感 形态 触感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此深得我心的茶杯 好久没遇到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是李边首的手艺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,让您见笑了 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:46.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,与大王的威严相配的\N果真是威仪的茶杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王室所用的瓷器就由李边首负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么会如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此鲜明的指痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:19.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 容臣妾说一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:25.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓦然一看 是很粗糙\N可越看越会觉得舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我想把那茶杯 占为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:33.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,确实是很粗燥的瓷器 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:39.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人也会被它那奇妙的洒脱感所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳边首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:48.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,日后寡人的专用瓷器就由你负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,谢主隆恩 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 王室专属瓷器是李边首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下专用瓷器是柳边首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这竞赛的结果是如何决定的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分院朗厅只会是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,二人中只选其一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:14.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,茶杯的优劣不是看卖相而是看功用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不如以品茶定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:22.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这杯茶就由恭嫔你来品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,谋 谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有人要谋害寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:05.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来人 内禁卫 内禁卫护驾 内禁卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,保护殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:12.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是不是你用的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:47.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,烧厨房和内医院都没发现毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:52.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,唯一值得怀疑之物就是茶杯上的釉粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:12:00.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,绝不宽饶 寡人绝不会宽饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:03.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,用了什么毒 是砒霜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:12.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下\N微臣制作的釉中绝没掺杂任何毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请相信微臣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:20.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嫔都倒下了\N你却谎称无毒 还要我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来人 把他拉出去斩首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 此事不能就这么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:35.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一介沙器匠\N绝不可能犯下此等滔天大案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是谁 谁是主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是谁指使你干的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣冤枉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果喝光这些釉就可证明微臣的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣甘之若贻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:08.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那不是中毒 是荨麻疹 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,荨麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:14.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嫔娘娘患有桃花荨麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:21.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,轻则会有搔痒症状\N重则会气血堵塞造成昏厥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:25.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,万幸娘娘已恢复了神智 正在静养中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:35.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混账 你在釉中加入了桃花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这都怪微臣失察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人意图谋害娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭请殿下治他谋逆之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,治他谋逆之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为什么要在釉中加入桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莫非你早就知道恭嫔患有桃花荨麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 微臣一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,釉中加入桃花是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一介沙器匠不可能知道娘娘的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:31.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣与柳边首共事多年\N他绝不是谋逆之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您明察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是谋逆之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既不是故意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:48.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,虽危机嫔妃之命 也就证明没有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是这个意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣惶恐 殿下 微臣只是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看错你了 李边首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,卿你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,虽然李边首有点僭越
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人还以为他是个只知道制陶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没想到他还很有眼色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这种气量分院交给他管理又有何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下真的这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:49.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,事情能这么圆满解决\N真是有如神助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:56.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嫔的荨麻疹您是怎么得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赏花时偶然得知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,健康时自不足虑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:08.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不过以现在快临产的虚弱身子骨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:18.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,任命李江天为分院郎厅\N务必尽心尽责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭喜您 朗厅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭喜您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,郎厅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小的有事相问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是因为釉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳边首大人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,朗厅大人 朗厅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说不行的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:45.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就一会儿 见个面就回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:46.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都怪我 大人才会受这种苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因为我制作的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:18.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下命我 制作御用茶器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:25.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你和我一起制作的茶器 越看越爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,越看越吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:30.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:35.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我害怕不能告诉你这些话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,总算了却了心事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我之所以要成为分院朗厅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是因为惜你之才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沙器匠之位不是一个女子可以僭越的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明知道这一点却不放弃梦想的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是那么的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:11.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,制作敬献给殿下的器物中\N胆敢掺入私心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,称我为谋逆之徒也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要在李朗厅手下苦练技艺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:25.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,登上分院沙器匠之位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你一定要成为朝鲜第一位女沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:37.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不管我身在何处 即便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不在此世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:48.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也会为你祈福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这么丑的茶杯\N竟然能入得了你的法眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下的眼光真是无人能及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:25.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果不是仁嫔娘娘 结果将完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:33.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,总而言之\N最后成为分院朗厅之人可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:44.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,与乙坦的恩怨就此勾销了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,担心乙坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不如担心怎么治理分院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:53.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不能再因此事引起任何风波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我说的话 希望你铭记於心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,朗厅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您为什么会送我桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:24.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,桃花可提高釉的黏度\N使之轻易黏附於器物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可配宣川白土的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别忘了是你自己找我来向我求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:35.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,收回其他白土 也是因为这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为了利用我制作可陷害乙憛大人的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你可不能乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这一切我要向义禁府告发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,命我在釉中加入桃花之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正是郎厅大人您 就这么告发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你敢谎报事实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,使用鬼蜮伎俩的是朗厅大人您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:22.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你心中不是怀有成为沙器匠的\N大志的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:28.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要因小失大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沙器匠之位我可...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为了成为沙器匠的梦想\N我坚忍到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,被大人蹂躏的那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:46.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也没有自绝坚忍到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我终於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:59.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有比柳边首大人更可贵的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你对他...对乙檀那人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爱慕著他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:16.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我岂敢喜欢柳边首大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我没有那资格 您应该比我更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:26.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若你敢说出釉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:31.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的性命 恐怕也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也要救柳边首大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:43.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等天一亮 我就去义禁府
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:52.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就连你这不起眼的女人也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:56.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀 乙檀 乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:09.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,马风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:29.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,阵痛已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.47,0:24:35.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我腹中的孩子是谁的\N你也很清楚不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:41.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢杀害你主人的血脉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:48.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去转告他\N这个孩子的胎梦是窑炉的大吉之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:49.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:02.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:05.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,窑炉的吉梦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:15.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他说绝对不能有弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.75,0:25:28.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果有弟弟妹妹\N就会被抢走所有的富贵权势和名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:30.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分明是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.39,0:25:33.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:42.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,毓道 怎么还没有睡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.77,0:25:46.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为了祝贺您 等著等著 刚才睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.18,0:25:49.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幸好听到大门的声音 醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:53.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,夜很深了 怎么不直接睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:56.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么能等到天亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:26:03.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父亲成为分院郎厅的事情\N真是让我高兴和自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:11.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,儿子也会努力成为能继承父亲的\N朝鲜第一的沙器匠的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.24,0:26:20.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然 快回去睡吧 毓道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:22.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.35,0:26:30.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的血脉毓道一个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.68,0:27:03.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 看看看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:15.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 恭嫔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.87,0:27:25.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,今天是好日子 除了重罪犯人之外
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:27.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赦免释放牢里所有的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.89,0:27:49.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,罪人 柳乙檀 免去边首一职\N从分院逐放
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.28,0:29:18.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉 你不是莲玉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:25.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.19,0:29:27.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么会在这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.23,0:29:30.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.07,0:29:32.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这孩子是...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.00,0:29:38.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:44.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是 乙檀大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:47.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没错 是我 不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.95,0:29:50.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:56.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 什么都不要问
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.13,0:30:00.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这个孩子 这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.16,0:30:03.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我得先叫医员
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.37,0:30:04.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.30,0:30:08.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,马上会有人追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.14,0:30:14.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 这个孩子 这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:18.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,追过来 谁会追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:20.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.86,0:30:33.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 我知道了\N先从这儿出去吧 把孩子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.83,0:30:37.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我的女儿 这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.87,0:30:43.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以后是要给主上殿下献上白瓷的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.74,0:30:50.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好吧 孩子给我 你也起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.71,0:30:52.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟我约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.55,0:31:00.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我出了什么事情\N就一定会守护这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.62,0:31:02.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,向我保证吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.09,0:31:05.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我保证 所以快起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.87,0:31:18.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.88,0:31:30.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.29,0:31:34.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:55.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:31:57.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.61,0:32:00.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子我会...莲玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.00,0:32:22.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.57,0:32:27.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为父为毓道你付出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.08,0:32:34.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你一定要成长为朝鲜最顶级的沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.29,0:32:43.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,吃得真香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.70,0:32:48.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎哟 瞧瞧 瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.04,0:32:55.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莲玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.50,0:32:57.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你在看著吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.44,0:33:00.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这个孩子是你的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.64,0:33:03.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:10.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也曾梦想著\N能有个将白瓷献给主上殿下的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:12.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:17.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,将这个孩子培养成\N朝鲜第一个女沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.46,0:33:24.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我真心 与你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.34,0:33:28.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎哟 瞧瞧 瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.64,0:33:32.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子他爹 你先看会儿孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.25,0:33:37.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.71,0:33:38.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.81,0:33:39.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.05,0:33:47.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎哟 你饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.09,0:33:52.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:33:57.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就这样 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.27,0:34:00.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎 当什么沙器匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:01.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.00,0:34:30.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,干嘛总是要做这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.57,0:34:33.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,甭管是谁做的\N到临了反正都要给砸碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.50,0:34:36.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到时候不还是再填填补补拿去卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:36.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.81,0:34:38.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,填补什么 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.27,0:34:40.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因为看著好端端的碗漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.48,0:34:43.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,酒家的大叔可没少发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.05,0:34:43.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.78,0:34:45.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏水吗 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:48.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 怎么会漏水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.92,0:34:50.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.02,0:34:51.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你没告诉我爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.85,0:34:53.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹还不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:56.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说是你卖出去多少碗就送出去三倍的数
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.63,0:34:59.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,老师好言相劝把人打发走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.03,0:35:02.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.87,0:35:03.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.97,0:35:05.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:08.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.68,0:35:23.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:25.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我在做陶瓷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.19,0:35:29.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,转过身来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.03,0:35:33.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,转过身来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.80,0:35:37.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哇 是箭哎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.07,0:35:46.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,慢慢地拉弓
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.74,0:35:49.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.85,0:35:51.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得看著靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:54.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,下巴尖 下脸颊 还有脖子这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.25,0:35:55.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,收拢双肩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:58.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 到底什么时候才射啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.29,0:36:00.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:00.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.86,0:36:03.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.73,0:36:08.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:10.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还是刀更快
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.13,0:36:11.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.87,0:36:13.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:16.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是朝鲜最棒的剑客柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.27,0:36:17.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,会伤著的 井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.74,0:36:18.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.21,0:36:21.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 会伤著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.75,0:36:30.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 很危险的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.86,0:36:41.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.80,0:36:45.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.63,0:36:47.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.77,0:36:52.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来了啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:56.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵啊 带著你爹先去房里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.65,0:36:58.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.85,0:36:59.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.95,0:37:02.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我都吩咐过让你悠著点 会有贵客来访
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.89,0:37:05.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么听我这当爹的话的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.92,0:37:08.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把这里收拾干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.76,0:37:10.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乖乖地待在你房里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:12.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.83,0:37:19.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然是跟朝鲜最棒的沙器匠学了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:21.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还有同门陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.24,0:37:24.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以说我这当爹的心里多踏实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:26.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.01,0:37:30.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟老师学习不知是何等的乐事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:32.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.08,0:37:35.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只不过什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.02,0:37:38.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说说看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.69,0:37:44.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有可竞争的同门 略感可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:50.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的意思是说\N我们井儿不是你的同门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.23,0:37:53.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿是这世上谁都无法取代的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.90,0:37:57.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是 她意不在陶瓷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.94,0:38:00.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以才觉得不是可竞争的同门
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:01.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:06.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此话倒是不假
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.75,0:38:08.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得有竞争对像
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.22,0:38:10.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,实力才有长进
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.52,0:38:14.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能走到边首这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.46,0:38:18.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也是因为有挚友和竞争对手的存在\N才能成为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:19.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:24.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就是分院郎厅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.83,0:38:27.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.30,0:38:29.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你出去 拿点米酒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:31.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.54,0:38:34.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:43.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天是位挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.45,0:38:46.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你当真如此想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.39,0:38:49.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当我深陷谋反罪之时 救我於水火的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:51.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,便是江天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:53.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,自你离开之后
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.00,0:38:54.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,诡异的传闻一直不断
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.83,0:38:55.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:59.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海君大人可还好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.60,0:39:01.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.17,0:39:04.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这对世间万象不感兴趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.01,0:39:06.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么就每次都如此关心大人的消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:09.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,多亏大人的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.14,0:39:12.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我才免於处斩 侥幸获得一命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.81,0:39:15.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,虽然未得见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.02,0:39:16.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但毕竟是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.85,0:39:18.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一直是如此想的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.14,0:39:39.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.98,0:39:41.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.08,0:39:42.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.25,0:39:52.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您找我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:53.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在出发开始狩猎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.56,0:39:55.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.02,0:39:56.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,定当铭记於心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.49,0:39:57.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:40:00.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不能跑在 我这个长子的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.00,0:40:03.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,理应如此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,另外此次狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.93,0:40:07.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不可捕获任何的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:11.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为何不作答
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.91,0:40:14.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既已来狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.11,0:40:15.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然就要狩猎了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.58,0:40:17.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:19.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你现在是要违抗我的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:21.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是要狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.45,0:40:22.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,断不是要赢过兄长的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:24.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您大可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.39,0:40:27.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要再三铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.34,0:40:50.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.18,0:40:52.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你为何要阻拦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.28,0:40:55.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那头鹿不是父王殿下的猎物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:58.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是想要在此次狩猎中\N展现兄长的气量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.52,0:41:00.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就要瞄准其他的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.36,0:41:02.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要走哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.29,0:41:04.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:06.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,深山处会有很多野兽的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.33,0:41:08.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.43,0:41:09.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您请先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:11.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不了 你来开路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.10,0:41:13.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.68,0:41:26.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你又要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.78,0:41:29.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 额...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.35,0:41:32.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 去采集白土
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:34.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.49,0:41:38.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我刚刚去酒家\N泰道哥哥说你要去狩猎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.16,0:41:40.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:42.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此事我可不知
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.93,0:41:45.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要在日落之前回来 我得赶紧走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.87,0:41:47.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.11,0:42:33.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不是早吩咐你不要狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.95,0:42:36.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-为何不等我\N-赶紧去抓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.89,0:42:40.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,已经中箭了 相信逃不了多远
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.29,0:42:42.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你今日坠马
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.76,0:42:44.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怕死狩不了猎了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.80,0:42:47.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.90,0:42:49.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.46,0:43:21.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么呀 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.66,0:43:23.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底是谁跟这儿挖的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.94,0:44:02.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,陷阱逮到什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:04.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.71,0:44:07.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蟒蛇 鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.64,0:44:10.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,陷阱是我提议挖的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:13.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以那里面的猎物都归我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.42,0:44:14.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道了吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.88,0:44:17.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你只是动动嘴皮子\N真正辛苦挖掘的可是我耶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:20.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.39,0:44:23.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你辛苦的时候 我又没闲著
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.33,0:44:24.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.98,0:44:45.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.71,0:44:47.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去逮住那只鹿再去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:50.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 不过陷阱里面的猎物都归我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.85,0:44:52.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不许反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.69,0:44:54.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以防万一 来 拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:02.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:05.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来逮到了一只大的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.00,0:45:09.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道是...老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.68,0:45:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.52,0:45:24.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.37,0:45:38.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你为何只顾著看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.20,0:45:40.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不快把我弄出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.77,0:45:42.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,原来不是猎物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.97,0:45:44.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.81,0:45:45.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.28,0:45:49.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道这陷阱是你挖的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.95,0:45:52.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对 我就是这陷阱的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.88,0:45:55.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,干嘛未经允许就擅自钻进去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.55,0:45:59.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等我上去 绝不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:46:01.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那请试著上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.99,0:46:06.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我...我说
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.93,0:46:09.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.40,0:46:11.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,起码得弄我出去再走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.97,0:46:13.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不快给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.45,0:46:27.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看您这上来会跟我拚命的架势\N我干嘛要救您吶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.75,0:46:29.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你可知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.95,0:46:33.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你若弃我不顾 一定会招来灭门之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.72,0:46:36.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是有够烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.93,0:46:39.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您就省点力气 安静呆著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.06,0:46:43.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,胳膊被蛇咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.00,0:46:48.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若不赶快治疗 毒会扩散到全身的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.67,0:46:50.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.61,0:46:53.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.81,0:46:54.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.38,0:46:57.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:19.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.87,0:47:21.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,连我都陷进来怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.70,0:47:22.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么出去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.80,0:47:24.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.37,0:47:26.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.11,0:47:27.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫你跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.58,0:47:29.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还是你跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.41,0:47:31.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那么等我出去之后会放绳子下来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.98,0:47:33.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫我如何相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.82,0:47:37.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我会出去喊军队来 跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:40.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此深山老林 还什么军队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:44.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来您中毒不轻啊 满嘴胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.83,0:47:48.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪条胳膊啊 得先处理蛇毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.53,0:47:54.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您撒谎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.10,0:47:58.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为了骗我 撒谎说被蛇咬伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.14,0:48:00.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:02.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是这条胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.35,0:48:14.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这...这可怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.92,0:48:17.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这毒都扩散到肩膀了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.13,0:48:18.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.43,0:48:24.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来 只好砍掉手臂了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.47,0:48:27.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这是在戏弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.77,0:48:29.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么戏弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.61,0:48:31.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都没被咬 怎么可能扩散...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.38,0:48:39.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,张口就撒谎 所以才会踩到\N这只有野兽才会踩的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.25,0:48:42.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大胆 你可知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.45,0:48:45.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟敢拿野兽与我相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.12,0:48:47.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我乃
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.99,0:48:55.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我乃本国的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.50,0:49:00.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您真的是王子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.44,0:49:04.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正是 还不快给我跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.57,0:49:08.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 小的罪该万死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.14,0:49:10.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您饶小的一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.35,0:49:13.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小的太过低贱 没能认出尊贵的您
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.65,0:49:16.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,罢了 不知者无罪 我宽宏...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.95,0:49:19.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以为我会这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.89,0:49:23.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟你说敬语 都觉得可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.19,0:49:23.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.93,0:49:26.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王子 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.86,0:49:28.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你骗过多少人了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.70,0:49:30.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就不怕遭天谴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:32.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.00,0:49:32.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.30,0:49:38.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你给我听好喽 我哥哥就快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.97,0:49:44.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若再敢撒谎\N我就叫哥哥只救我 把你撇在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.11,0:49:45.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.68,0:49:49.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很好 到时候一定会被灭三族
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.25,0:49:51.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.09,0:49:52.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 好害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.92,0:49:55.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以为吓我 我就不敢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.23,0:49:59.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 快来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.90,0:50:01.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这里一个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.73,0:50:04.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 泰道哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.70,0:51:07.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.57,0:51:14.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是我的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.40,0:51:15.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.50,0:51:18.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这确实是我的箭 您为何这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.44,0:51:22.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 看不到肚子上的箭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.85,0:51:25.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是没射中要害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.05,0:51:28.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是被我射中脑袋死的\N所以这只野猪是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.45,0:51:30.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这家伙竟敢...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.92,0:51:36.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再加上这支箭与您的箭不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.53,0:51:41.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您看 与您的颜色完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.93,0:51:45.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还愣著做什么 还不给我绑了这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.23,0:51:46.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.74,0:51:54.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放开我 我到底做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.15,0:52:09.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说的哥哥呢 到底甚么时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你确定他会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:16.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你确定有哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.43,0:52:17.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.63,0:52:23.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定是打了条大猎物 来得慢罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.41,0:52:24.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.97,0:52:29.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那我出去找你哥哥来 跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.28,0:52:32.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你又没见过他 怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.95,0:52:35.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算出去 也得是我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.88,0:52:38.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,该跪下的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.19,0:52:40.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.66,0:52:42.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可是一国王子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.33,0:52:47.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是不能跪下的身子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.63,0:52:50.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,世上哪有不能跪下的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.93,0:52:54.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,两条胳膊往前伸 膝盖像这样跪著
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.60,0:52:55.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:07.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,滚开 你这无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.39,0:53:11.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.49,0:53:13.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对呀 你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.32,0:53:15.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以别跟我这种无礼之徒待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.89,0:53:17.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快把我弄出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.73,0:53:20.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不是还有哥哥来找你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.03,0:53:23.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来你想逃跑 这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.97,0:53:27.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等从这里出去 就押你去官衙\N等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.64,0:53:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,官衙
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.84,0:53:32.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真是自掘坟墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.04,0:53:35.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这可是你说的 到时候可别怨我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.34,0:53:38.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是我要说的话 还是担心你自个儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.68,0:53:44.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥怎么还不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.36,0:53:48.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.74,0:54:11.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这个小偷 你这还算是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.68,0:54:13.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这一生都得偷下去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.62,0:54:15.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:26.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.36,0:54:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一箭未射却夺人猎物\N怎么能算得上是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.60,0:54:38.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一箭未射 你很好奇我的射术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:42.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 我就亲自射给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.91,0:55:17.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.19,0:55:27.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.49,0:55:30.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.96,0:55:35.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 那个 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.00,0:55:36.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.10,0:55:36.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.91,0:55:48.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不赶紧跪下 这位是主上殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.31,0:55:51.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放肆 你这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.55,0:55:58.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因为看不到珲儿 所以我一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.49,0:56:02.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但是这家伙\N带著插有珲儿箭矢的猎物出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.16,0:56:03.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿的箭矢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.63,0:56:05.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 父王
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.09,0:56:10.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人举止古怪 怕是否加害於珲儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.97,0:56:13.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以我正在进行审问
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.17,0:56:14.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你加害於他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.74,0:56:19.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 我根本就不知道他是谁\N也没见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:21.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是把那只受伤的野猪...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.24,0:56:26.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王 我将继续审问 查出珲儿的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.75,0:56:28.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您允许
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.36,0:56:35.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,老板 我们的汤饭怎么还不送上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.19,0:56:37.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-稍微等一下嘛...\N-来了 马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.76,0:56:39.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,金泰道的父亲是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.33,0:56:43.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是我啊 出什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.63,0:56:45.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,马上把这家伙抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.47,0:56:46.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.20,0:56:50.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-为什么啊...\N-大人 为什么抓人啊... -老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.35,0:57:03.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.45,0:57:04.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-爹\N-泰道
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.92,0:57:05.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.76,0:57:07.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.59,0:57:11.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底是何罪名 竟然连我爹也抓来了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.53,0:57:13.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我们是无辜的 我们冤枉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.00,0:57:16.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴 安静地等候殿下的发落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.03,0:57:19.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.23,0:57:22.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 这可真是晴天霹雳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.64,0:57:26.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿呢 逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.31,0:57:29.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我说 请帮我叫大人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.81,0:57:39.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我们仔细搜查了酒肆\N当光海君大人并不再那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.05,0:57:41.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这也算报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.62,0:57:45.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是不能马上找回来\N我就要砍了兼司仆将你的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.66,0:57:46.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.76,0:57:52.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王 我要通过那家伙把珲儿找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.94,0:57:58.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不是不知道他是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.51,0:58:01.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,虽然我不认识大人\N但我对这座山了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.44,0:58:05.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我能在天黑前找到大人\N那就请您放了我和我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.11,0:58:11.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 不过如果找不到\N我就要对你实施惩罚了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.14,0:58:31.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥做得挺好啊 我怎么就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.54,0:58:34.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么这么冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.11,0:58:36.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以为我生火是因为闲得没事干么
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.31,0:58:39.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这里可是大夏天也会结冰的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.25,0:58:41.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就赶紧生火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.29,0:58:45.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要是行 你就试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.88,0:59:09.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.45,0:59:12.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你打算冻死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.65,0:59:17.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这可是之前在森林里迷路时\N救了我哥和我性命的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.52,0:59:22.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,常言道 男女七岁不同席\N你这是何古怪之举
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.19,0:59:25.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这无礼的家伙\N还想顾及自己的体面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.23,0:59:29.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,俗话说 好死不如赖活著
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.90,0:59:32.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是不想被冻死就老实地待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:51.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.65,0:59:55.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是按照你说的做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.59,0:59:57.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.26,1:00:32.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可以感受到温热 看来可以撑下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.40,1:00:35.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你往那边点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.60,1:00:40.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,干嘛啊 我可不想被冻死呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.44,1:00:51.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混账 你都对我做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.11,1:00:54.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.32,1:00:59.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我又没跑步 心脏为何跳得这么快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.13,1:01:04.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你笑什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.53,1:01:10.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别光顾著笑 赶紧回答我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.24,1:01:21.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那是因为你被我迷住了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.95,1:01:29.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,迷住 我被你迷住吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.35,1:01:57.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.81,1:01:59.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 您在哪儿啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:00.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:02.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 您在哪儿啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.22,1:02:03.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.26,1:02:07.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.72,1:02:09.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,终於来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.93,1:02:12.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,听那一阵马蹄声\N肯定是我的军士们来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.86,1:02:16.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你看 我说过他们肯定会来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.00,1:02:21.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 难道说...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.14,1:02:30.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真的是大人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.67,1:02:52.13,Next2,,0,0,0,,*下集预告*
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.13,1:02:56.54,Next2,,0,0,0,,万一一是百姓对王子大人大声咒骂\N还动手打他
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.54,1:02:58.01,Next2,,0,0,0,,那会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.01,1:02:59.47,Next2,,0,0,0,,我要马上对你处斩
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.47,1:03:02.04,Next2,,0,0,0,,您说忘情定要找到一个人见到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.04,1:03:04.61,Next2,,0,0,0,,木剑对真剑可不合适
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.61,1:03:05.71,Next2,,0,0,0,,我不想再见到您了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.71,1:03:07.18,Next2,,0,0,0,,你倒是抗辩一下啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.18,1:03:08.28,Next2,,0,0,0,,我怕再见面时又会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.28,1:03:10.49,Next2,,0,0,0,,将光海任命为分院的副提调
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.49,1:03:12.69,Next2,,0,0,0,,万万不可啊 殿下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.69,1:03:14.52,Next2,,0,0,0,,制造一个丰饶祭上使用祭器吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.52,1:03:16.73,Next2,,0,0,0,,我将奉御命制造祭器
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.73,1:03:21.13,Next2,,0,0,0,,只要我还是朗厅 你就休想涉足分院
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.13,1:03:23.33,Next2,,0,0,0,,您是谁 为何如此胡言乱语
